dcterms:description: The COHA corpus is composed of documents dating from 1810 to 2009 and contains over 400 million words. The genre mix of the texts is balanced in each decade, and includes fiction works, academic papers, newspapers, and popular magazines.
dcterms:title: Corpus of Historical American English (COHA)
